## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **adalimumab Humira 2016** = first FDA biologic noninfectious uveitis — VISUAL-I + VISUAL-II + VISUAL-III trials. paradigm shift from corticosteroid + classical immunosuppressive 1L 이래. quantum-VQE 의 TNF-α pocket 직접 fit.
2. **dexamethasone Ozurdex 2010** = first FDA intravitreal sustained-release implant — 0.7mg 6mo duration. 만성 noninfectious posterior + intermediate uveitis + DME + RVO macular edema. systemic steroid 부작용 회피.
3. **fluocinolone Iluvien 2014 + Yutiq 2018** = sustained-release intravitreal — 36mo duration. 만성 chronic noninfectious posterior uveitis. cataract + IOP 부작용 monitoring 필요.
4. **dexamethasone Dextenza 2018** = 만성 intracanalicular punctum insert — postop ocular pain + 만성 dry eye + 만성 ocular surface allergic conjunctivitis. drug delivery innovation.
5. **voclosporin Lupkynis 2021** = first FDA novel calcineurin inhibitor LN approval — research uveitis Phase 3 ongoing. cyclosporine A 대비 PK + safety profile improved.
6. **tocilizumab IL-6R off-label uveitis** = STOP-uveitis trial + retrospective evidence — refractory uveitis 에서 효과. cross-systemic_sclerosis_specific + inflammatory_arthritis IL-6R pathway 공유. quantum-VQE 의 IL-6R pocket cross-leverage.
7. **rituximab anti-CD20 off-label uveitis** = refractory + 만성 자가면역 uveitis — case series + small RCT. cross-bone_marrow_failure CD20 mechanism 공유.
8. **secukinumab + ixekizumab IL-17A research** = Phase 3 mixed result — IL-17A pathway uveitis 일부 이차 sub-population 효과. cross-psoriasis_specific 동일 pathway.
9. **methotrexate JIA-uveitis 소아 1L** = 소아 idiopathic juvenile arthritis 동반 uveitis — methotrexate maintenance + adalimumab 후속. 한국 K-uveitis framework 동일.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, uveitis 임상 의미 한정. adalimumab 의 systemic 부작용 + 만성 ocular delivery 한계 가 hxq-uve-il6r-001 의 design rationale.

